body:
How good was it to see Legacy match it with the Chiefs on the weekend. All I have been hearing is how the Chiefs are by far the standout team in the region,  I really enjoyed seeing Legacy not only match it with the Chiefs in the first game, but then come out even stronger in the second game to take the series 2-0 with a dominating performance.

Well Done Legacy - Keep it up!

